msgctxt "mn81:6.13"
msgid "Tatiyampi kho, ānanda, jotipālo māṇavo ghaṭikāraṃ kumbhakāraṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "For a third time, Jotipāla said to him, "

msgctxt "mn81:6.14"
msgid "‘alaṃ, samma ghaṭikāra. "
msgstr "‘Enough, dear Ghaṭīkāra. "

msgctxt "mn81:6.15"
msgid "Kiṃ pana tena muṇḍakena samaṇakena diṭṭhenā’ti? "
msgstr "What’s the use of seeing that baldy, that fake ascetic?’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
# NOTE: See my note on AN 3.70.
#. VAR: ādāya → āhara (mr)
#. VAR: sottisināniṃ → sottiṃ sināniṃ (bj, pts1) | sottisinānaṃ (s1-3, km, mr)
msgctxt "mn81:6.16"
msgid "‘Tena hi, samma jotipāla, sottisināniṃ ādāya nadiṃ gamissāma sināyitun’ti. "
msgstr "‘Well then, dear Jotipāla, let’s take some bathing paste of powdered shell and go to the river to bathe.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "mn81:6.17"
msgid "‘Evaṃ, sammā’ti kho, ānanda, jotipālo māṇavo ghaṭikārassa kumbhakārassa paccassosi. "
msgstr "‘Yes, dear,’ replied Jotipāla. "

msgctxt "mn81:6.18"
msgid "Atha kho, ānanda, ghaṭikāro ca kumbhakāro jotipālo ca māṇavo sottisināniṃ ādāya nadiṃ agamaṃsu sināyituṃ. "
msgstr "So that’s what they did. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya7, pts-vp-pli2.47, sc4
msgctxt "mn81:7.1"
msgid "Atha kho, ānanda, ghaṭikāro kumbhakāro jotipālaṃ māṇavaṃ āmantesi: "
msgstr "Then Ghaṭīkāra addressed Jotipāla, "

msgctxt "mn81:7.2"
msgid "‘ayaṃ, samma jotipāla, kassapassa bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa avidūre ārāmo. "
msgstr "‘Dear Jotipāla, the Buddha Kassapa’s monastery is not far away. "

