msgctxt "mn81:8.9"
msgid "Atha kho, ānanda, ghaṭikāro kumbhakāro jotipālaṃ māṇavaṃ ovaṭṭikāyaṃ parāmasitvā etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Ghaṭīkāra grabbed Jotipāla by the belt and said, "

