#. VAR: vinivaṭṭetvā → viniveṭhetvā (bj, s2, s3, km, pts1) | vinivedhetvā (s1)
msgctxt "mn81:8.13"
msgid "Atha kho, ānanda, jotipālo māṇavo ovaṭṭikaṃ vinivaṭṭetvā ghaṭikāraṃ kumbhakāraṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "So Jotipāla undid his belt and said to Ghaṭīkāra, "

