#. VAR: sīsaṃnhātaṃ → sasīsaṃ nahātaṃ (bj) | sīsanhātaṃ (s1-3, km) | sīsanahātaṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "mn81:8.16"
msgid "Atha kho, ānanda, ghaṭikāro kumbhakāro jotipālaṃ māṇavaṃ sīsaṃnhātaṃ kesesu parāmasitvā etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Ghaṭīkāra grabbed Jotipāla by the hair of his freshly-washed head and said, "

msgctxt "mn81:8.17"
msgid "‘ayaṃ, samma jotipāla, kassapassa bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa avidūre ārāmo. "
msgstr "‘Dear Jotipāla, the Buddha Kassapa’s monastery is not far away. "

msgctxt "mn81:8.18"
msgid "Āyāma, samma jotipāla, kassapaṃ bhagavantaṃ arahantaṃ sammāsambuddhaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamissāma. "
